  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/0383893b188c5edac6e34fd850f6b74b.webp?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serial Cleaner is a fast-paced stealth action game set in 1970s America where you play as a professional mob cleaner. Your job is to dispose of the bodies, clean away blood stains and hide evidence - all while avoiding the police.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay out of sight, work quickly and make sure no trace of the crime remains. A good cleaner never gets caught!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/9986e9d7c613872e80f154bcd7831436.webp?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it's stowing them in your wagon or tossing them off a skyscraper - make sure those bodies don't see the light of day!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/e4365fec63bf0d3fc6652e6eda7ff366.poster.avif?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/e4365fec63bf0d3fc6652e6eda7ff366.webm?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/e4365fec63bf0d3fc6652e6eda7ff366.mp4?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/2aa6de6efa5af73c5ab424488a493865.webp?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who knew bodies had so much blood?... Vacuum up as much as you can to ensure the police don't suspect a thing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/ed1f43d153d43785bd9431ed1b99359a.poster.avif?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/ed1f43d153d43785bd9431ed1b99359a.webm?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/ed1f43d153d43785bd9431ed1b99359a.mp4?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/fde0615545a05cb3c9885ee5da38fce0.webp?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Murder weapon left behind? Incriminating documents left scattered? Whatever it is, make sure the police don't get to it before you do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/9f7eb67ec3ba0306f750e7fed87304ee.poster.avif?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/9f7eb67ec3ba0306f750e7fed87304ee.webm?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/9f7eb67ec3ba0306f750e7fed87304ee.mp4?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/8cd4d9fa5dcc6da93b63977598cb72cb.webp?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The best cleaners are never seen or heard, so use every trick at your disposal to hide and avoid getting caught!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/b0168dc336273fb80153e36e0c57ebca.poster.avif?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/b0168dc336273fb80153e36e0c57ebca.webm?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/b0168dc336273fb80153e36e0c57ebca.mp4?t=1749737711\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/522210/extras/62dd36ac7fcba2203a9befb04168d320.webp?t=1749737711\" width=616 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– Twenty story-driven contracts to complete in the 70s-inspired campaign</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– Eleven themed outfits to unlock</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Clean up and jive to the funky 70s inspired soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– Multiple 'Challenges' for each campaign contract with community leaderboards</p>",
